(389, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Nicola Isabel Gilmour\",\"slug\":\"nicola-isabel-gilmour\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Year 3 Class Teacher\\r\\nPost Graduate Diploma in Education, University of Glasgow, Scotland.\\r\\nBachelor of Arts (Honours) in Journalism, Edinburgh Napier University, Scotland.\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Nicola Isabel Gilmour<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/nicola.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n<section itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\">\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Year 3 Class Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Post Graduate Diploma in Education, University of Glasgow, Scotland.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Bachelor of Arts (Honours) in Journalism, Edinburgh Napier University, Scotland.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Nikki joins us from Scotland, where she has been teaching full-time. She has experience teaching children from age 5-11 and has a real passion for teaching reading and writing. She is now looking forward to extending her teaching experience in an international setting. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Nikki undertook a work placement in Ghana during her time at University, which sparked her love of travelling and living overseas. She enjoys learning about new cultures, visiting interesting places and meeting the local people. Nikki has been settling into life in Vietnam very well and has been particularly enjoying trying the amazing Vietnamese food. In her spare time Nikki enjoys keeping fit by swimming and doing Yoga.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/nicola.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 40, 'Nicola Isabel Gilmour', 'info', '2020-02-21 03:01:57', '2020-02-21 03:01:57'),
(390, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Jack Odam\",\"slug\":\"jack-odam\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Year 2 Class Teacher\\r\\nBA Hons Primary Education with English specialism \\u2013 University of Chichester, England.\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Jack Odam<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/jack-odam.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Year 2 Class Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>BA Hons Primary Education with English specialism &ndash; University of Chichester, England.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Jack comes to Saigon Star straight from England where he has taught the last 3 years in Years 1 and 2 and led English as a subject for one year. Whilst in sixth form college Jack began working 1 afternoon a week in a Primary School which sparked his love and passion for teaching. He immediately began applying for a teaching degree which he then went on to complete. Jack would describe himself as an energetic, passionate and fun teacher who enjoys both building relationships with his children and challenging them in their learning. Jack&rsquo;s aim is to make all learning fun and create a learning environment in which everyone makes mistakes and learns from them.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Jack enjoys playing football in his spare time. He is looking forward to exploring Vietnam and other places in South East Asia during his time with us at Saigon Star.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/jack-odam.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 41, 'Jack Odam', 'info', '2020-02-21 03:03:55', '2020-02-21 03:03:55'),
(391, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Emer Taheny\",\"slug\":\"emer-taheny\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Bachelor of Education Degree, Mary Immaculate College, Limerick, Ireland.\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Emer Taheny<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/emer-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n<section itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\">\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Year 2 Class Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Bachelor of Education Degree, Mary Immaculate College, Limerick, Ireland.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Emer comes to us from County Mayo which is on the west coast of Ireland. She graduated from Mary Immaculate College in 2016 and since then she has been teaching 2 years full-time in Dublin and this will be her second-year teaching in Saigon Star International School, Vietnam.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Emer is very excited to be a part of the Primary teaching team this year, having taught Pre-School last year. Emer fits into the Saigon Star internationally-minded community very well, having studied various modules in college with an international perspective and having taught in Kolkata, India during her studies too.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Being an educational practitioner has always been Emer&rsquo;s dream and she loves to ignite her children&rsquo;s interests through various teaching methodologies but particularly through the Creative Arts. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Emer would describe herself as passionate, creative and innovative when it comes to her teaching; her main goal is to make sure her children are learning in a fun and meaningful way and she pays particular attention to the nurturing of each child in their talents and abilities.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In her free time, Emer loves to explore Vietnam, sampling all of the delicious food and traditions it has to offer. She has a real passion for travelling but when she&rsquo;s not on a plane you&rsquo;ll find her outdoors and playing sports. One of her favorite sports is Irish Gaelic Football; she plays it here in Ho Chi Minh City as part of the Saigon Gael&rsquo;s Irish Gaelic Football team.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/emer-1.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 42, 'Emer Taheny', 'info', '2020-02-21 03:05:11', '2020-02-21 03:05:11'),
(392, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Yasmeen Russul Saib\",\"slug\":\"yasmeen-russul-saib\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Year 6 Class Teacher\\r\\nBA (Hons) in Primary Education, Manchester Metropolitan University, UK\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Yasmeen Russul Saib<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/yasmeen.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n<section itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\">\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Year 6 Class Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>BA (Hons) in Primary Education, Manchester Metropolitan University, UK<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Though a qualified Primary Teacher, Yasmeen began her teaching career in an inner-city Secondary School in Moss Side, Manchester as the SEN Transition Teacher working with Year 7 and 8 pupils.&nbsp;For 4 years, she taught a class of pupils with a range of special educational needs.&nbsp;After a few years, she also acquired leadership positions as Curriculum Area Leader of Transition and Primary Liaison Leader.&nbsp;Prior to her teaching career, she worked as a Legal Secretary for an International Law Firm in London.&nbsp;Yasmeen has experience teaching in Yangon, Myanmar where she taught Year 5 in a British International School.&nbsp;Recently, she has been teaching in a British Preparatory School in Hong Kong as the English and Science specialist to Years 5-8.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Through her teaching approach, she believes in creating an inclusive, exciting and stimulating classroom environment so pupils can flourish by allowing opportunities for creativity, building confidence and encouraging a passion for learning.&nbsp;Her main interests outside of the classroom are reading, travelling, exercise and spending time with her nieces and nephew.&nbsp;She is also a qualified Zumba Instructor.&nbsp;Yasmeen is really excited to be living in Vietnam and being a part of the Saigon Star family!&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/yasmeen.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 43, 'Yasmeen Russul Saib', 'info', '2020-02-21 03:07:03', '2020-02-21 03:07:03'),
(393, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Alexandra Martinez\",\"slug\":\"alexandra-martinez\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Bachelors of Science in Education,\\u00a0University of\\u00a0 Vermont.\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Alexandra Martinez<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/alex.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n<section itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\">\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Middle Years Class Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Bachelors of Science in Education,&nbsp;University of&nbsp; Vermont.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Alex graduated in 2013 with Bachelors of Science in Education, specifically focusing in the Middle School Years. She has a Professional Educators license from the state of Vermont endorsed in Middle Level Mathematics.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Alex began her education career in the outdoor education field, where she taught all over the state of California. She would spend a week at a time with different schools, teaching about the specific environment they were in, survival skills and leading various outdoor activities. This job opened the world for Alex and it led her to an amazing opportunity on a little island off the coast of Malaysia. There she continued her work in outdoor education, working with international schools from Singapore and Malaysia.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>From Malaysia, Alex made her way to Vietnam to work in a traditional classroom setting. For the past three years, she has been teaching mathematics at international schools in Ho Chi Minh City. She is very excited to start her first year teaching at Saigon Star!&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>When Alex is not teaching, she is can be found cooking and eating, travelling and exploring new places and outdoor activities!&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/alex.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 44, 'Alexandra Martinez', 'info', '2020-02-21 03:09:24', '2020-02-21 03:09:24'),
(394, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Neil Maclean\",\"slug\":\"neil-maclean\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Middle Years Class Teacher\\u00a0(English specialism)\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Neil Maclean<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/neilmaclean-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n<section itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\">\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Middle Years Class Teacher&nbsp;(English specialism)<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>BA (hons) History, Durham University; MA (hons) filmmaking, Leeds Metropolitan University; PGCE with QTS English, University College London.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Originally from the United Kingdom, Neil first worked as an English teacher internationally after graduating from University and then worked for several years in media and publishing before returning to the UK, and teaching five years ago.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Neil has now decided to combine his passion for educating with travelling and exploring new cultures. He loves helping students improve their communication skills, express their creativity and push the limits of their knowledge.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In his spare time, Neil enjoys playing sports, visiting new places and taking photographs.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/neilmaclean-1.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 45, 'Neil Maclean', 'info', '2020-02-21 03:10:24', '2020-02-21 03:10:24'),
(395, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Faith Gamo dela Cruz\",\"slug\":\"faith-gamo-dela-cruz\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Bachelor of Science in Nursing, Philippines. Passed the Nursing Licensure Exam in 2011\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Faith Gamo dela Cruz<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/montessori.jpg\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n<section itemprop=\\\"articleBody\\\">\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Montessori Class Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Bachelor of Science in Nursing, Philippines. Passed the Nursing Licensure Exam in 2011<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Diploma in Montessori (Early Years), AMI.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>After graduating in college, Ms. Faith joined various medical missions in the Philippines to gain more experience in her field. In 2011-2013, she worked for Korean language centers hoping to support her Masters in the future.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>She moved to Vietnam in 2013 and worked for Saigon star as a School nurse and Learning Assistant. She then fell in love with Montessori and decided to learn more of this specialism under the guidance of the excellent Ms. Adrienne.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With her passion and dedication, she completed her AMI- Children&rsquo;s House Assistant Course in University of Social and Humanities, VNU-HCM, and got her diploma in Montessori teacher training (early years).<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Inspired by her nephew with special needs, Faith is reading books and articles on how to introduce Montessori to children with ASD, global delays and other learning disabilities.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/montessori.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 46, 'Faith Gamo dela Cruz', 'info', '2020-02-21 03:11:58', '2020-02-21 03:11:58'),
(396, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Rachael\\u00a0Collins\",\"slug\":\"rachael-collins\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"BA Hons in English Literature, University of Brighton, England.\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\"><b>Rachael&nbsp;Collins<\\/b><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/rachael.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">EAL Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>BA Hons in English Literature, University of Brighton, England.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>CELTA, International House Belfast.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Rachael&nbsp;originates from Ireland but has also lived in England, Spain and now Vietnam.In order to pursue a career in teaching,&nbsp;Rachael&nbsp;moved to Madrid, Spain, in 2014 in order to teach English as an Additional Language. During her time there, she taught a range of students using a teaching method that was designed to help students increase their agility with the language and communicate in correct English, but within a fun and dynamic learning environment.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Rachel later moved to Granada, Spain in 2016 to gain more experience and work in an official Cambridge examination centre where she prepared Young Learners of English to take the official Cambridge Examination and taught intensive courses which involved speaking, listening, reading, writing and grammar practice.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Over the summer of 2019&nbsp;Rachael&nbsp;completed the CELTA course in order to achieve the most widely recognised qualification for teaching English as a second language. The multicultural aspect of the course inspired and motivated&nbsp;Rachael&nbsp;to teach further afield, leading to her decision to move to Vietnam in September 2019.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>When not teaching,&nbsp;Rachael&nbsp;enjoys travelling, horse riding and photography.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/rachael.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 47, 'Rachael Collins', 'info', '2020-02-21 03:14:19', '2020-02-21 03:14:19'),
