(471, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"q0qMMSHHUNttZMXqYdUB5ceWeUlAI6JQk7ermcTM\",\"name\":\"About us\",\"slug\":\"about-us\",\"slug_id\":\"70\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"At the Saigon Star international school, learning and personal growth\\r\\ncontinue long after the day\\u2019s lessons have ended. We aim to provide our students with\\r\\nopportunities to develop their natural talents, build confidence, practice a healthy lifestyle\\r\\nand expand their world view.\",\"content\":\"<h4><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><b>1. <span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Mission<\\/span><\\/b><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<blockquote>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"font-style: italic; text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">&quot;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong>To be recognised, externally, as a leading IPC school.<strong><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">&quot;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<\\/blockquote>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><b>2.<span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/b><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\"><strong>Our Shared Vision<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\\\">Our core belief at Saigon star is that education should help children to develop a balance of academic achievement and personal qualities.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\\\">that will support them as life-long learners and enable them to contribute in meaningful ways to our rapidly-changing ,global society<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"467\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/batdongsan.local\\/storage\\/general\\/vision-150x150.jpg\\\" width=\\\"700\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\">As one of the most family-friendly international schools in Ho Chi Minh City Vietnam, we understand that for parents, the single most important factor when choosing a school is the school&#39;s shared vision. Above all else, it is the most influential factor in determining the type of person a child will become. To be truly effective, a shared vision is one that is shared not only among teachers, but among parents and learners, so that we are all working towards the same goal. Here&#39;s ours:.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\">Our core belief at Saigon Star is that education should help children to develop a balance of academic achievement and personal qualities, that will support them as life-long learners and enable them to contribute in meaningful ways to our rapidly-changing, global society..<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Intelligence plus character &ndash; that is the true goal of education.&rdquo; -Martin Luther King Jr.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"general\\/vision-150x150.jpg\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 3, 'About us', 'primary', '2020-02-24 00:02:02', '2020-02-24 00:02:02'),
(472, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"q0qMMSHHUNttZMXqYdUB5ceWeUlAI6JQk7ermcTM\",\"name\":\"Admissions\",\"slug\":\"admissions\",\"slug_id\":\"80\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"adm\",\"content\":\"<h1 class=\\\"titlepg\\\">Admissions Process<\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"contentpg\\\">\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Admission is granted to a student when it has been determined that the School has an appropriate programme and resources to meet that individual&rsquo;s learning needs. Applications for both immediate and future entry are considered at any time throughout the year.&nbsp;<\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The birth date cut-off for placement in a particular grade is 31st August in the academic year (commencing in August) of admission. The child must have turned the appropriate age on or prior to 31st August for the grade in question.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"color: #008080;\\\"><strong>Visit Us<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We recommend that all families visit our campus to find out whether our friendly school community represents a good fit fot you child.&nbsp;<\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Our school office is open and available to assist you with inquiries, school tours and enrolments Monday to Friday, from 07:30 to 16:30 throughout the year, including during school holidays.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"color: #008080;\\\"><strong>How to Apply<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Please <a href=\\\"#\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ff6600;\\\"><u>complete the online inquiry form and then application form<\\/u><\\/span><\\/a><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. The online application portal will prompt you to submit the following supporting documents:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 4