uo;s &lsquo;shared vision&rsquo; is so important when choosing a school.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Regarding our mission, this can be broken down into two parts: for children to be safe and successful.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We define&nbsp;<span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">&lsquo;<b>safe<\\/b>&rsquo;&nbsp;<\\/span>as being both physically safe and emotionally safe. We define&nbsp;&lsquo;<span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\"><b>successful<\\/b><\\/span>&rsquo;&nbsp;as experiencing daily success in learning, making meaningful contributions to society, and developing the attitudes and skills of a lifelong learner.<\\/p>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"general\\/vision-150x150.jpg\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/80.0.3987.122 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 3, 'About us', 'primary', '2020-03-01 22:18:46', '2020-03-01 22:18:46'),
