(861, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"GTzzViLUIIjdL4NHMp93pe3gG5SRdxdP6mI6lrVX\",\"name\":\"About us\",\"slug\":\"about-us\",\"slug_id\":\"70\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"At the Saigon Star international school, learning and personal growth\\r\\ncontinue long after the day\\u2019s lessons have ended. We aim to provide our students with\\r\\nopportunities to develop their natural talents, build confidence, practice a healthy lifestyle\\r\\nand expand their world view.\",\"content\":\"<h4><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><b>1. <span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">Our Mission<\\/span><\\/b><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<blockquote>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"font-style: italic; text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">&quot;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span>To provide a safe and supportive learning environment, and every opportunity for children to be successful both as learners and as contributors in a changing world&quot;<\\/h2>\\r\\n<\\/blockquote>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><b>2.<span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/b><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\"><strong>Our Shared Vision<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Responsible global citizens<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"467\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/batdongsan.local\\/storage\\/general\\/vision-150x150.jpg\\\" width=\\\"700\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><b>3.<\\/b><strong><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">Our Shared Vision &amp; Mission Explained<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Beyond the influence of parents in the home, a child&rsquo;s education is the single most important factor in determining the type of person a child will become;&nbsp;&nbsp;that is why it is a school&rsquo;s &lsquo;shared vision&rsquo; is so important when choosing a school.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Regarding our mission, this can be broken down into two parts: for children to be safe and successful.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We define&nbsp;<span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">&lsquo;<b>safe<\\/b>&rsquo;&nbsp;<\\/span>as being both physically safe and emotionally safe. We define&nbsp;&lsquo;<span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\"><b>successful<\\/b><\\/span>&rsquo;&nbsp;as experiencing daily success in learning, making meaningful contributions to society, and developing the attitudes and skills of a lifelong learner.<\\/p>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"general\\/vision-150x150.jpg\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/81.0.4044.113 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 3, 'About us', 'primary', '2020-04-22 20:59:29', '2020-04-22 20:59:29'),
