(13, 'Teaching & Learning in Action', '<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"335\" src=\"http://batdongsan.local/storage/primaryyears/library.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Learning Support</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><i>Are you an education professional seeking to design innovative courses that &lsquo;blend&rsquo; different sorts of media learning activities across time and space? Do you find it challenging to decide what might be the best blend of activities and media for effective learning? In an age where innovations in social computing and the mainstreaming of e-tools are unlocking new opportunities for blending online with face-to-face interactions, this book will help you to design and implement effective blended e-learning</i></p>', '[\"middleyears\\/classroom-03.jpg\",\"middleyears\\/classroom-05.jpg\",\"primaryyears\\/library.jpg\",\"primaryyears\\/hinhnen3.jpg\"]', 'Su Hy Nhan Street, Thanh My Loi Ward, District 2 Ho Chi Minh City', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '2020-02-09', '2020-02-09', 'selling', '2020-02-09 02:15:36', '2020-02-09 02:23:04', 0, 'Are you an education professional seeking to design innovative courses that ‘blend’ different sorts of media learning activities across time and space?', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 3),
